{"sections":[],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"ComposableArchitecture"}],"title":"Migrating to 1.14","roleHeading":"Article","role":"article"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/migratingto1.14"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"As the library prepares for Swift 6 we are in the process of updating the library’s APIs for","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"sendability and isolation where appropriate, and doing so in a backwards compatible way. Prior","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to version 1.14 of the library the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" type has only ever been meant to be used on the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"main thread, but that contract was not enforced in any major way. If a store was interacted with","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"on a background thread a runtime warning would be emitted, but the compiler had no knowledge of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the type’s isolation.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"That now changes in 1.14 where "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is now officially "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@MainActor"},{"type":"text","text":"-isolated. This has been"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"done in a way that should be 100% backwards compatible, and if you have problems please open a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"http:\/\/github.com\/pointfreeco\/swift-composable-architecture\/discussions","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"However, if you are using ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"strict"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" concurrency settings in your app, then there is one circumstance","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in which you may have a compilation error. If you are accessing the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"store"},{"text":" in a view method or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property in Xcode <16, then you may have to mark that property as ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@MainActor"},{"text":":","type":"text"}]},{"syntax":"diff","type":"codeListing","code":[" struct FeatureView: View {","   let store: StoreOf<Feature>"," ","   var body: some View {","     \/\/ ...","   }"," ","+  @MainActor","   var title: some View {","     Text(store.name)","   }"," }"]}],"kind":"content"}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.19","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.18","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17.1","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.16","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.15","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.13","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.12","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.11","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.10","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.9","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitec